## Important constraints
- Never crash on a single scraper failure — wrap each source in try/except, log error, continue
- Rate limit: add 1–2 second delay between API calls
- LLM call timeout: 10 seconds max, skip scoring if timeout (score = 0, reason = "scoring failed")
- SQLite writes must be thread-safe (use check_same_thread=False + a threading lock)


